<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Customer Order</title>
    <style>
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            font-size: 10px;
        }

        header,
        section,
        footer {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .container header {
            display: flex;
            gap: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header .border {
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
        }

        header p {
            margin: 5px;
        }

        header .logo {
            width: 30%;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .reciever-heading {
            display: flex;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .reciever-heading p {
            width: 50%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .reciever-heading .border {
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .consignee-heading {
            display: flex;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .consignee-heading p {
            width: 50%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .consignee-heading .border {
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
        }

        header .company-details {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 40px;
        }

        h1,
        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .tax-invoice {
            display: flex;
            padding-inline: 10px;
        }

        .tax-invoice .tax {
            text-align: center;
            width: 70%;
        }

        .reciever {
            display: flex;
        }

        .reciever .border {
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .reciever .receiver-details {
            width: 50%;
            padding-inline: 10px;
        }

        .reciever .invoice-details {
            width: 50%;
            padding-inline: 10px;
        }

        .reciever .invoice-details .details {
            display: flex;
        }

        .reciever .invoice-details .details .dates {
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            justify-content: start;
            margin-right: 10px;
            margin-left: 200px;
        }

        .reciever .invoice-details .details .text {
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        p {
            margin-block: 5px;
        }

        .receiver-details .text {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .receiver-details .text .text-title {
            width: 15%;
        }

        .receiver-details .text .text-details {
            width: 75%;
        }

        .consignee {
            display: flex;
        }

        .consignee .border {
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .consignee .consignee-details {
            width: 50%;
            padding-inline: 10px;
        }

        .consignee .despatch-details {
            width: 50%;
            padding-inline: 10px;
        }

        .consignee .despatch-details .details {
            display: flex;
        }

        .consignee .despatch-details .details .dates {
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            justify-content: start;
            margin-right: 10px;
            margin-left: 200px;
        }

        .consignee .despatch-details .details .text {
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .consignee-details .text {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .consignee-details .text .text-title {
            width: 15%;
        }

        .wmproducts{
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .consignee-details .text .text-details {
            width: 75%;
        }

        .product-details table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .product-details th {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 30%;
        }

        .product-details td {
            padding: 8px;
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .product-details th:first-child,
        .product-details td:first-child {
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .product-details tbody td:not(:last-child) {
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .product-details td:nth-child(2) {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .product-details tfoot td {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .product-details .small-column {
            width: 5%;
        }

        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            display: flex;
        }

        footer .border {
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        footer .terms {
            width: 70%;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        footer .footer-logo {
            width: 30%;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .bill-amount {
            border-bottom: none;
            display: flex;
        }

        .bill-amount .amount-details {
            width: 70%;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .bill-amount .total {
            width: 30%;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
        }

        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 8px;
        }

        .sub-column {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .sub-column span {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .bill-amount table .large {
            width: 20%;
        }

        .bill-amount table .medium {
            width: 15%;
        }

        .bill-amount table .small {
            width: 10%;
        }

        .bill-amount .border {
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .bill-amount .total .total-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .bill-amount .total .grand-total {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 130px;
        }

        .bank-details {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="data:image/png;base64,"
                    alt="smit-alluminium-logo" />
            </div>
            <div class="border"></div>
            <div class="company-details">
                <h1>SMIT ALLUMINIUM</h1>
                <p>
                    C-19,Bhagyodaya Part-2,Nand Bunglow Road, Ghatlodiya,
                    Ahmedabad, GODOWN : 259/2/2, B /H. Kitchen Express,, Nr. Indian Gas
                    Godown, Santej Vadsar Road, SANTEJ
                </p>
                <p>Contact : E-Mail : smitalluminum@ymail.com</p>
                <p>
                    GSTIN : 24AIMPP7660D1Z3, PAN NO. : AIMPP7660D, State : Gujarat, Code
                    : 24
                </p>
            </div>
        </header>
        <section class="tax-invoice">
            <p><b>GSTIN</b> : 24AIMPP7660D1Z3</p>
            <p class="tax"><b>Tax Invoice</b></p>
        </section>
        <div class="reciever-heading">
            <p>Details of Receiver (Billed to)</p>
            
        </div>
        <section class="reciever">
            <div class="receiver-details">
                <div class="text">
                    <p class="text-title"><b>Name</b></p>
                    <p class="text-details">: {{customer.name}}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <p class="text-title"><b>Address</b></p>
                    <p class="text-details">
                        : {{customer.address_line1}},
                        {{customer.address_line2}}, {{customer.city}},
                        {{customer.state}}, {{customer.zipcode}}
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <p class="text-title"><b>Mob. No.</b></p>
                    <p class="text-details">: {{customer.phone}}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <p class="text-title"><b>Email ID</b></p>
                    <p>: {{customer.email}}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <p class="text-title"><b>State</b></p>
                    <p class="text-details">: {{customer.state}}, Code : {{customer.zipcode}}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <p class="text-title"><b>GST No.</b></p>
                    <p class="text-details">: {{customer.gst_number}}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <p class="text-title"><b>Order No.</b></p>
                    <p class="text-details">: {{customerOrderNumber}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
           
            
        </section>
        
        <section class="product-details">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th class="small-column">Serial Number</th>
                        <th>Product Name</th>
                        <th class="small-column">Coating</th>
                        <th class="small-column">Color</th>
                        <th class="small-column">Product Code</th>
                        <th class="small-column">Quantity</th>
                        <th class="small-column">Pcs</th>
                        
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each entries}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{inc @index}}</td>
                        <td>{{product.name}}</td>
                        <td>{{coating.name}}</td>
                        <td>{{color.name}}</td>
                        <td>{{product.productCode}}</td>
                        <td>{{calcTotalWeight product.weight quantity}} KG</td>
                        <td>{{quantity}} Pcs</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
                <tfoot>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td style="font-weight: 700;">Estimate Weight: </td>
                        <td>{{getEstimateWeight entries}}</td>
                        <!-- Adjust this value according to the total amount -->
                    </tr>
                </tfoot>
            </table>
        </section>
        {{#if wmproducts}}
        <section class="product-details wmproducts">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th class="small-column">Serial Number</th>
                        <th colspan="3">Customer's Product Name</th>
                        <th class="small-column">Pcs</th>                        
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each wmproducts}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{inc @index}}</td>
                        <td colspan="3">{{product}}</td>
                        <td>{{quantity}} Pcs</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
                {{!-- <tfoot>
                    <tr>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <!-- Adjust this value according to the total amount -->
                    </tr>
                </tfoot> --}}
            </table>
        </section>
        {{/if}}
        <div class="bank-details">
            <p>BANK DETAIL : Deutsche Bank (C.G. ROAD BRANCH )</p>
            <p>A/C. NO : 100040767690019</p>
            <p>IFSC CODE : DEUT0406PBC</p>
        </div>
        <footer>
            <div class="terms">
                <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>
                <p>1- OUR RISK & RISPONSIBILITYCASES OF GOODS FROM OUR PREMISES.</p>
                <p>
                    2 - GOODS ONCE SOLD WILL NOT BE TAKEN BACK UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTACES.
                </p>
                <p>
                    3 - INTEREST WILL BE CHARGED 24% PER ANNUME IF NOT PAID WITHIN 7
                    DAYS
                </p>
                <p>4 - SUBJECT TO AHMEDABAD JURISDICTION ONLY.</p>
                <p>5 - THIS IS A COMPUTER GENERATED INVOICE.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 40px">
                    RECEIVER SIGNATORY _________________________________
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border"></div>
            <div class="footer-logo">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Unde maiores
                odio magni eaque delectus est rerum recusandae aliquam, blanditiis
                doloribus, distinctio ut, hic libero officiis qui quibusdam? Tempora
                iure error laborum, adipisci, ea ducimus voluptatibus soluta neque
                sunt optio, ipsam praesentium perferendis perspiciatis dolore libero
                unde enim eius nobis tenetur.
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>

</html>